videos.description: Tim Hardaway Jr. comes up with the steal and trots down the court to throw down an uncontested fast-break dunk at the end of the first quarter.

videos.headline: Hardaway gets the steal and the slam for Dallas

videos.description: James Harden first discards Tim Hardaway Jr. with a step-back move as he nails a jumper, then Harden hits a 3-pointer in Luka Doncic's face and draws contact for the foul.

videos.headline: Harden schools Hardaway and Luka

videos.description: Luka Doncic humbly explains to Rachel Nichols that despite what some valid NBA authorities are saying, he can't be compared to Larry Bird at this point in his career.
